{"tid":1409470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！！連登被大量3毛帶風向！！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T21:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:07:47.000Z","uid":179014,"like":46,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba6d1a373c9b35fa3889ca21a25f9f2f9ad467f","tid":1409470,"uid":179014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:41:25.000Z","msg":"坦白講，我都無咩資格開呢個post，我個AC都係P牌 (但明明用左好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但岩岩睇左個幾鐘頭 Post，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">發現大量 Post 已經俾3毛入侵兼洗版！！</span></strong></span>帶風向既程度比之前係嚴重好多好多！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉個例子：<br />\n&gt;&gt;&gt; 呢一刻開始，我地要用致命武力 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1409151/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1409151/page/1</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GUbfseV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGUbfseV.png&h=fc39cb48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不分化好重要，但呢個 Post 已經唔係兄弟爬山咁簡單，我無辦法認同，不過呢個唔係重點，重點係內裡有大量 3毛 P 牌帶風向：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVOtM3s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVOtM3s.png&h=91a1dab3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣係咪即係鼓吹只要抱住好彩唔俾人拉到既心態就無問題？再詳細睇個AC，全部post都係煽動仇警，真正重要既五大訴求／其它話題甚少提及：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvB3AYy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvB3AYy.png&h=2db8d7cd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxbvfYO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxbvfYO.png&h=529b00b8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住唔洗一陣，就有其它 P 牌推 Post：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbXipT3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbXipT3.png&h=c711f7bd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n順手起底：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKbSukQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKbSukQ.png&h=0e09b59d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來又係一個白雪雪咩都無既 3毛 account<br />\n<br />\n呢排真係好多好多好多P牌，唔排除有人真係呢排關心多左時事，所以開AC，但睇post時真係要好小心，唔好懶，見到啲極重情感既 post 同留言 (仇警/失敗論/分化)，起左底先。<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多個 Post 都係咁樣，大家小心啦"},{"pid":"879a6f35dc6994c489f01e3c856fbb328249a162","tid":1409470,"uid":149566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6z1yYmX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6z1yYmX.jpg&h=e20c9467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罷罷罷"},{"pid":"2ede52bb0d092662cd35ee468be375525f030bd4","tid":1409470,"uid":173191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:50:47.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n覺得可疑就起底睇清楚<br />\n最好做埋google search <br />\n唔好戇鳩鳩咁俾人帶風向 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三毛早晨呀！準備去艱苦地區參軍同捐器官未？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"797bce0924dac061894b5088f08ffb9fe325aaf2","tid":1409470,"uid":179014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f56e3884be3be5ee79e703f8e3ac38df52193295","tid":1409470,"uid":28677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:56:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b96416049d5b02cc61706f84bfcf90dd29faf37e","tid":1409470,"uid":137527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:57:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4333f20747d9838b5d0bb67b2a6903c42dc9420","tid":1409470,"uid":67718,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:00:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母<br />\n如果比人除底褲嗰個係係老婆女朋友係你個女<br />\n你仲講唔講得岀呢啲野啊<br />\n依家班狗已經係做咩都唔會有後果<br />\n你就仲係到諗有咩和平既方法對付佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af7c56296944dab3ba3f6b23dc623896ff7f521","tid":1409470,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite